Submodules¶

GPyOpt.util.quadrature.emin_epmgp module¶

GPyOpt.util.quadrature.emin_epmgp.emin_epmgp(m, K, eta)[source]¶

This is a wrapper function for the matlab function emin_epmgp that calculated the expectation of a Gaussian vector with mean m and covariance K and a costant eta.
